{{Vgname|1=她的故事|en=Her Story}}是{{le|萨姆·巴洛|Sam Barlow}}设计开发的[[互动式电影|电影游戏]]。游戏于2015年6月24日登陆[[Microsoft_Windows|Microsoft Windows]]、[[OS_X|OS X]]和[[iOS|iOS]]平台，6月25日登陆[[Android|Android]]平台。在游戏中，玩家须筛选出虚构警察审讯片段数据库视频，以解决一名男子失踪的案件。审讯聚焦于由英国音乐人{{le|薇娃·塞弗特|Viva Seifert}}饰演的男子妻子汉娜·史密斯。

本作是巴洛离开[[Climax_Studios|Climax Studios]]转型为{{le|独立电子游戏开发|Independent video game development|独立开发人}}的首个项目。他希望开发一款仰赖剧情的游戏，直至想出可行的概念才着手创作。巴洛最终决定打造{{le|警方程序|Police procedural}}游戏，融入[[全动态影像|全动态影像]]。为此，他观看了现存的警方采访，展开研究。期间，他发现了嫌犯回答中有重复的主题，便决定将歧义纳入游戏的调查中。

一经发行，游戏便获得许多评论家的称赞，尤其是叙事、角色表现和突破传统的游戏机制方面。游戏售出10万多份，获多项年终奖提名，包括众多{{le|游戏媒体|Video game journalism}}的{{le|年度游戏奖列表|List of Game of the Year awards|年终游戏奖}}。

== 玩法 ==

《她的故事》是一款[[互动式电影|互动式电影]]游戏，聚焦于七段1994年的警方[[审讯|审讯]]<ref name="IGN">{{cite web |url=http://ign.com/articles/2015/06/03/her-story-is-an-fmv-adventure-coming-to-pc-and-ios-on-june-24 |title=Her Story is an FMV Adventure Coming to PC and iOS on June 24 |last=Rad |first=Chloi |work=IGN |publisher=Ziff Davis |date=2015-06-03 |accessdate=2016-01-16 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6eZfdLRJz?url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2015/06/03/her-story-is-an-fmv-adventure-coming-to-pc-and-ios-on-june-24 |archivedate=2016-01-16 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。游戏开头，一台装有数个文件和程序的旧[[桌面环境|台式机]]呈现在玩家面前<ref name="Guardian">{{cite web |url=http://www.theguardian.com/technology/2015/feb/27/her-story-computer-game-true-detective-meets-google |title=Her Story: the computer game where True Detective meets Google |last=Stuart |first=Keith |work=The Guardian |publisher=Guardian Media Group |date=2015-02-28 |accessdate=2016-01-14 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6eWpR7Gjr?url=http://www.theguardian.com/technology/2015/feb/27/her-story-computer-game-true-detective-meets-google |archivedate=2016-01-14 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，内置解释游戏机制的教学文本文档<ref name="Adventure Gamers Review">{{cite web |url=http://www.adventuregamers.com/articles/view/28898 |title=Her Story review |last=Smith |first=Katie |publisher=Adventure Gamers |date=2015-07-03 |accessdate=2016-01-16 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6eZZxWVOq?url=http://www.adventuregamers.com/articles/view/28898 |archivedate=2016-01-16 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。在桌面上自动打开的程序“L.O.G.I.C. Database”允许玩家搜索并排列数据库内的271条视频短片<ref name="GamesRadar">{{cite web |url=http://www.gamesradar.com/making-her-story/ |title="I'd always been reluctant to go indie" – The story behind Her Story |author=Edge |work=GamesRadar |publisher=Future plc |date=2015-09-29 |accessdate=2016-01-16 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6eYi9tYfe?url=http://www.gamesradar.com/making-her-story/ |archivedate=2016-01-15 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref name="Digital Spy Review">{{cite web |url=http://www.digitalspy.com/gaming/review/a654320/her-story-review-play-detective-in-this-profound-gripping-live-action-interactive-drama/ |title=Her Story review: Play detective in this profound, gripping live-action interactive drama |last=Donnelly |first=Joe |work=Digital Spy |publisher=Hearst Corporation |date=2015-06-22 |accessdate=2016-01-16 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6eZZlw00t?url=http://www.digitalspy.com/gaming/review/a654320/her-story-review-play-detective-in-this-profound-gripping-live-action-interactive-drama/ |archivedate=2016-01-16 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。短片是警方对英国女子汉娜·史密斯（{{lang|en|Hannah Smith}}）的审讯，但无法观看全片，玩家只能观看片段<ref name="Pocket Gamer preview">{{cite web |url=http://www.pocketgamer.co.uk/r/iPhone/Her+Story/news.asp?c=65811 |title=Hands-on with Her Story – an entrancing cold case detective game |last=Brown |first=Mark |work=Pocket Gamer |publisher=Steel Media |date=2015-06-11 |accessdate=2016-01-16 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6eZfiC3Hj?url=http://www.pocketgamer.co.uk/r/iPhone/Her+Story/news.asp?c=65811 |archivedate=2016-01-16 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。汉娜在审讯中回答未出镜警探的未知问题，玩家须破译答案的内容<ref name="PC Gamer 2">{{cite web |url=http://www.pcgamer.com/the-story-behind-her-story/#page-2 |title=The story behind Her Story |page=2 |last=Clark |first=Tim |work=PC Gamer |publisher=Future plc |date=2015-07-09 |accessdate=2016-01-14 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6eVfK9aOK?url=http://www.pcgamer.com/the-story-behind-her-story/#page-2 |archivedate=2016-01-13 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。汉娜的回答已完成转录，玩家需用转录的词汇搜索数据库寻找短片。玩家选择短片时，需输入筛选搜索结果的标签。而桌面上的数据库检查器程序，则允许玩家重播看过的短片，短片看過后，数据库检查器内的红框变绿<ref name="Digital Spy Review" />。桌面还出现改编自战略棋盘游戏《[[黑白棋|黑白棋]]》的小游戏《镜子游戏》（{{lang|en|''Mirror Game''}}）<ref name="Guardian guns">{{cite web |url=http://www.theguardian.com/technology/2015/jul/14/her-story-murder-games-naomi-alderman |title=Her Story has no guns or finish line, just a search for meaning in an uncertain world |last=Alderman |first=Naomi |work=The Guardian |publisher=Guardian 