== 剧情 ==
审讯录像展现一名声称丈夫西蒙失踪的女子汉娜·史密斯（{{le|薇娃·塞弗特|Viva Seifert}} 饰）。后来据证实西蒙（{{lang|en|Simon}}）遇害。汉娜承认两人关系紧张，但吵架后她去了[[格拉斯哥|格拉斯哥]]，因而有[[不在场证明|不在场证明]]。随着审讯的多个细节批露出來，發現“汉娜”实际上是两名[[双胞胎#同卵双生（identical_twins）|同卵双生双胞胎]]女子汉娜和伊娃（{{lang|en|Eve}}）。当时接生的助产士弗洛伦丝是一位退伍军人遗孀，她想要个孩子，但不想再婚，便谎称伊娃夭折，把伊娃带回自家抚养。8年以来，双胞胎并不知道彼此的存在，直至有一天，弗洛伦丝不幸滑下楼梯身亡，伊娃才从她的日记中发现了事情的真相。伊娃去到汉娜家，汉娜把她藏在她家的阁楼上，她们决定以一个人的身份保存一本共同的日记及一套以“汉娜”的身份定义她们行为的规则<ref name="Walkthrough">{{cite web |url=http://www.pocketgamer.co.uk/r/iPhone/Her+Story/feature.asp?c=66078 |title=Her Story explained – the complete story walkthrough (Spoilers!) |last=Brown |first=Mark |work=Pocket Gamer |publisher=Steel Media |date=2015-06-25 |accessdate=2016-01-14 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6eWFA4q8G?url=http://www.pocketgamer.co.uk/r/iPhone/Her+Story/feature.asp?c=66078 |archivedate=2016-01-14 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

汉娜最终开始跟{{le|玻璃工|Glazier}}同事西蒙约会。汉娜打破姐妹俩的规矩，与西蒙睡觉时搞大了肚子。按照规则，伊娃也应该怀孕，这样姊妹两人看上去才会一样，但她拼尽全力都未能如愿怀孕。8个月的时候，汉娜流产。多年后，西蒙在酒吧碰到伊芙。两人开始了外遇，伊娃怀孕，而汉娜由于流产的并发症却[[不孕|不孕]]。姐妹俩生日当天，西蒙送给汉娜一面手工定制的镜子，但汉娜透露她有一个怀孕的姐妹，他是孩子的父亲时，两人陷入争吵。第二天，伊娃与他吵架后离开格拉斯哥。汉娜戴着伊芙的假发跟西蒙会面。西蒙并不知道她是汉娜，送给她另一面镜子。怒不可遏的汉娜打碎镜子，但飞溅的镜子碎片意外射进西蒙的喉咙，杀死了他。伊娃回家后，两人一致同意藏匿西蒙的尸体，利用伊芙去格拉斯哥作为不在场证明<ref name="Walkthrough" />。审讯最后，伊娃指出汉娜“已失踪”<ref>{{cite video game |title=Her Story |developer=Sam Barlow |date=2015-06-24 |platform=Microsoft Windows |version=1.0 |scene=D769 |quote=My sister is gone. And she's never coming back. }}</ref>，要求跟律师讲话<ref>{{cite video game |title=Her Story |developer=Sam Barlow |date=2015-06-24 |platform=Microsoft Windows |version=1.0 |scene=D771 |quote=I'd like to speak to a lawyer now. }}</ref>。

玩家足以揭开故事真相时，会有对话框询问玩家是否完成解谜，一旦作出肯定回答，就会透露玩家是伊娃的女儿莎拉（{{lang|en|Sarah}}）。对话问莎拉是否理解母亲的行为，并要求莎拉到外面见她<ref>{{cite video game |title=Her Story |developer=Sam Barlow |date=2015-06-24 |platform=Microsoft Windows |version=1.0 }}</ref>。

== 开发 ==
[[File:Sam_Barlow_headshot_(cropped).png|thumb]]

本作由此前在[[Climax_Studios|Climax Studios]]参与《[[寂静岭：起源|寂静岭：起源]]》（2007）和《[[寂静岭：破碎记忆|寂静岭：破碎记忆]]》（2009）等游戏创作的{{le|萨姆·巴洛|Sam Barlow (video game director)}}开发。供职于Climax Studios，巴洛便萌生了警方角度游戏的概念，但为了开发出的游戏“扎根于剧情”<ref name="Edge">{{cite web |url=http://www.edge-online.com/news/why-climaxs-sam-barlow-is-going-independent-to-develop-crime-fiction-title-her-story/ |title=Why Climax's Sam Barlow is going independent to develop crime fiction title Her Story |last=Long |first=Neil |work=Edge |publisher=Future plc |date=2014-05-06 |accessdate=2016-01-14 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140516123945/http://www.edge-online.com/news/why-climaxs-sam-barlow-is-going-independent-to-develop-crime-fiction-title-her-story/ |archivedate=2014-05-16 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，便决定成为独立制作人<ref name="Develop"/>。开发商把[[厨槽现实主义|厨槽现实主义]]作为拒绝游戏推销的主要原因让巴洛深感沮丧，他发现独立能让他创作属于自己的互动式电影游戏作品<ref name="Vice">{{cite web |url=http://www.vice.com/read/watching-as-detectives-the-truth-behind-her-story-400 |title=Watching as Detectives: The Truth Behind 'Her Story' |last=Porter |first=Matt |work=Vice |publisher=VICE Media LLC |date=2015-07-01 |accessdate=2016-01-15 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6eXBnUac4?url=http://www.vice.com/read/watching-as-detectives-the-truth-behind-her-story-400 |archivedate=2016-01-14 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。早在玩过《{{le|漫漫旅途|Year Walk}}》和《[[80days|80days]]》等游戏后，他还希望独立<ref name="Gamesindustry">{{cite web |url=http://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/2015-07-10-investigating-her-story |title=Investigating Her Story |last=Horneman |first=Jurie |work=Gamesindustry.biz |publisher=Gamer Network |date=2015-07-13 |accessdate=2016-01-15 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6eYN8VP1V?url=http://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/2015-07-10-investigating-her-story |archivedate=2016-01-15 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。直至想出可行的概念，他从着手开发。他表示：“如果做一部探索式恐怖游戏，我可能完成得很轻松......不过我清楚，预算原因可能会带来巨大的妥协<ref name="Develop"/>。”巴洛将他的积蓄投入到游戏的制作中，留给他一年的开发时间<ref name="GamesRadar"/>。随后他构思游戏的概念，认为它应聚焦于“温馨的环境、对白和任务互动”，而这是大作经常回避的方面<ref name="Develop"/>。1999年，他的游戏《{{le|走道|Aisle (video game)}}》受到源源不断的支持后，创作本作的想法灵光一闪<ref name="Gamesindustry"/>。提到本作打破游戏惯例的办法时，巴洛将本作与电影创作运动[[道格玛95|道格玛95]]和[[阿尔弗雷德·希区柯克|阿尔弗雷德·希区柯克]]1948年电影作品《[[夺魂索|夺魂索]]》相比<ref name="Virgin">{{cite web |url=http://virginmediagaming.egxlondon.net/articles/her-story-as-told-by-sam-barlow |title=Her Story, as told by Sam Barlow |author=EGX |work=Virgin Media |publisher=Liberty Global |date=2014-08-03 |accessdate=2016-01-16 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6eYjbPdyA?url=http://virginmediagaming.egxlondon.net/articles/her-story-as-told-by-sam-barlow |archivedate=2016-01-15 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

游戏获得[[Steam|Steam青睐之光]]项目支持及{{le|Indie Fund|Indie Fund}}[[群众募资|群众募资]]，于2015年6月24日登录[[Microsoft_Windows|Microsoft Windows]]、[[OS_X|OS X]]和[[iOS|iOS]]平台<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.polygon.com/2015/6/3/8718713/serial-style-mystery-her-story-release-date |title=Serial-style mystery game Her Story launches June 24, watch the new trailer here |last=Farokhmanesh |first=Megan |work=Polygon |publisher=Vox Media |date=2015-06-03 |accessdate=2016-01-14 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6eWmrSR5J?url=http://www.polygon.com/2015/6/3/8718713/serial-style-mystery-her-story-release-date |archivedate=2016-01-14 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。巴洛本想全平台同步发行游戏，但对玩家的反应不太确定<ref name="Pocket Gamer">{{cite web |url=http://www.pocketgamer.biz/feature/62104/making-of-her-story/ |title=Howdunnit: The making of Her Story |last=Mckeand |first=Kirk |work=Pocket Gamer |publisher=Steel Media |date=2015-10-13 |accessdate=2016-01-14 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6eWHdw9Zk?url=http://www.pocketgamer.biz/feature/62104/making-of-her-story/ |archivedate=2016-01-14 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。他表示：“如果我只在一个平台发行，就会失去许多潜在的观众<ref name="App Unwrapper">{{cite web |url=http://www.appunwrapper.com/2015/07/10/help-interrogate-sam-barlow-about-her-story/ |title=Interrogating "Her Story" Creator Sam Barlow and Actress Viva Seifert (Interview) |page=1 |publisher=App Unwrapper |date=2015-07-10 |accessdate=2016-01-14 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6eWlsbLXV?url=http://www.appunwrapper.com/2015/07/10/help-interrogate-sam-barlow-about-her-story/ |archivedate=2016-01-14 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。”在移动设备上游玩本作，对他来说是“‘沙发式’体验”<ref name="MCV">{{cite web |url=http://www.mcvuk.com/news/read/his-story-sam-barlow-on-creating-one-of-this-year-s-most-talked-about-indie-hits-her-story/0153443 |title=His Story: Sam Barlow on creating one of this year's most talked-about indie hits, Her Story |last=Jarvis |first=Matthew |work=Market for Home Computing and Video Games |publisher=Intent Media |date=2015-07-30 |accessdate=2016-01-15 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6eYPJSzko?url=http://www.mcvuk.com/news/read/his-story-sam-barlow-on-creating-one-of-this-year-s-most-talked-about-indie-hits-her-story/0153443 |archivedate=2016-01-15 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。他也指出移动设备经常用来看视频上网，在这上面发行游戏“很正常”，而游戏玩法更是利用了相类似的任务<ref name="MCV"/>。让他对在移动平台上发布游戏疑虑的是，[[iPhone|iPhone]]的640×480像素比800×600要小。然而一番测试过后的好评鼓励他在移动平台发行<ref name="App Unwrapper"/>。开发几近完成时，[[游戏测试|游戏测试]]进行，使得巴洛“平衡了某些方面”，“一同润色了物件”<ref name="Taylor Holmes">{{cite web |url=http://taylorholmes.com/2015/01/24/her-story-game-interview-with-sam-barlow/ |title=Her Story Game Interview With Sam Barlow |last=Holmes |first=Taylor |publisher=THiNC |date=2015-01-24 |accessdate=2016-01-16 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6eYZUYPlA?url=http://taylorholmes.com/2015/01/24/her-story-game-interview-with-sam-barlow/ |archivedate=2016-01-15 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。[[Android|Android]]版于2016年6月29日发布<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2016-06-29-her-story-makes-its-way-to-android | title = Her Story makes its way to Android | first = Martin | last = Robertson | date = 2016-06-29 | accessdate = 2016-06-29 | work = Eurogamer | archive-date = 2016-06-30 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160630163144/http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2016-06-29-her-story-makes-its-way-to-android | dead-url = no }}</ref>。游戏运行于[[Unity_(游戏引擎)|Unity]][[游戏引擎|游戏引擎]]<ref name="gamasutra road igf">{{cite web |url=http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/266014/Road_to_the_IGF_Sam_Barlows_Her_Story.php |title=Road to the IGF: Sam Barlow's Her Story |last=Wawro |first=Alex |work=Gamasutra |publisher=UBM TechWeb |date=2016-02-17 |accessdate=2016-02-17 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6fNA5rktD?url=http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/266014/Road_to_the_IGF_Sam_Barlows_Her_Story.php |archivedate=2016-02-17 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

=== 玩法设计 ===
[[File:Her_Story_screenshot_04.jpg|thumb]]的技术挑战让巴洛感到失望后，他决定将真人动画镜头加入游戏<ref name="PC Gamer 1">{{cite web |url=http://www.pcgamer.com/the-story-behind-her-story/ |title=The story behind Her Story |page=1 |last=Clark |first=Tim |work=PC Gamer |publisher=Future plc |date=2015-07-09 |accessdate=2016-01-14 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6eVfFClI6?url=http://www.pcgamer.com/the-story-behind-her-story/ |archivedate=2016-01-13 |deadurl=no }}</ref>]]
巴洛的最开始的想法是创作一款警方审讯题材的游戏，却“并不清楚确切的做法”<ref name="Pocket Gamer"/>。之后他设想加入真实的录像和利用数据库界面查阅录像的能力。他表示界面“一部分是[[Apple_II|Apple II]]，一部分是[[Windows_3.1|Windows 3.1]]，一部分是[[Windows_98|Windows 98]]”<ref name="Pocket Gamer"/>。界面设计的灵感源于巴洛对警察游戏流派的赞赏，他表示“让计算机本身成为游戏中道具的这一想法非常简明<ref name="Guardian"/>。”他还比较了游戏中的搜索机制和[[Google|Google]]，希望实现“玩家本质上用谷歌搜索”的构想<ref name="Guardian"/>。游戏概念受电视连续剧《{{le|情理法的春天|Homicide: Life on the Street}}》启发，巴洛发现他所刻画的警方询问是“侦探的角斗场”<ref name="Develop"/>。巴洛故意“稍微拉长”游戏的开场画面，及时提醒玩家将要遵循缓慢的节奏<ref name="Fantastic Arcade">{{cite speech |url=https://vimeo.com/144009779 |title=Sam Barlow on the origins of HER STORY |last=Barlow |first=Sam |event=Fantastic Arcade |place=Austin, Texas |date=2015-10-01 |accessdate=2016-01-17 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6eanSJL3T?url=https://vimeo.com/144009779 |archivedate=2016-01-17 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

创作游戏的灵感源于巴洛对同类侦探游戏的失望，他认为《[[黑色洛城|黑色洛城]]》从未让他感觉自己像“察颜观色且思维缜密的优秀侦探”，表示《[[逆转裁判系列|逆转裁判]]》系列“死板”<ref name="Eurogamer">{{cite web |url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2015-02-09-her-story-is-a-desktop-thriller-true-detective-fans-can-get-behind |title=Her Story is a "desktop thriller" True Detective fans can get behind |last=Yin-Poole |first=Wesley |work=Eurogamer |publisher=Gamer Network |date=2015-02-09 |accessdate=2016-01-14 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6eWrMEeoM?url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2015-02-09-her-story-is-a-desktop-thriller-true-detective-fans-can-get-behind |archivedate=2016-01-14 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。巴洛着手开发游戏时加入更多传统的游戏概念，但随着开发的进展，游戏机制愈发简练<ref name="RPS">{{cite web |url=http://www.rockpapershotgun.com/2015/01/23/text-lies-and-videotape-her-story-interview/ |title=Text, Lies And Videotape: Her Story Interview |last=Smith |first=Adam |work=Rock, Paper, Shotgun |date=2015-01-23 |accessdate=2016-01-14 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6eWZfzb3X?url=http://www.rockpapershotgun.com/2015/01/23/text-lies-and-videotape-her-story-interview/ |archivedate=2016-01-14 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。最初的计划是让玩家朝着最终的解决方案努力，直至破解案件。不过，当巴洛在现存的已定罪谋杀犯{{le|克里斯托弗·帕尔科|Christpoher Porco}}询问笔录中测试了这一概念时<ref name="PC Gamer 2"/>，才开始探寻从询问中浮现的主题，尤其是跟帕尔科审判的一大关键因素钱有关的概念<ref name="Kotaku">{{cite web |url=http://www.kotaku.co.uk/2015/07/10/the-real-murder-behind-her-story |title=The Real Murder Behind Her Story |last=Benson |first=Julian |work=Kotaku |publisher=Gawker Media |date=2015-07-10 |accessdate=2016-01-14 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6eWoAYdHG?url=http://www.kotaku.co.uk/2015/07/10/the-real-murder-behind-her-story |archivedate=2016-01-14 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。他记下这一主题和线索重复出现的概念，决定在开发时“超越明显照本宣科的元素”<ref name="PC Gamer 2"/>。他认为侦查的模糊性催生出剧情的吸引力，还比较了游戏与他在开发后期听过的播客《Serial》。他指出，“人们偏向于某些解释......让它变得有趣的元素便是它存活于你的想象中的程度”<ref name="PC Gamer 2"/>。

=== 剧情与角色 ===
[[File:Viva_Seifert,_Rough_Trade_East_2009.png|thumb]]

巴洛对他此前的项目，尤其是将演员表演转制成游戏引擎的技术挑战感到懊恼后，决定将真人画面加入游戏<ref name="PC Gamer 1"/>。尽管预算较多，巴洛还是很享受供职于Climax Studio时亲自寻找游戏演员的经历<ref name="Develop"/>。他利用《{{le|凯恩的遗产：迟暮艳阳|Legacy of Kain: Dead Sun}}》取消前一年的间歇期联系到{{le|薇娃·塞弗特|Viva Seifert}}<ref name="PC Gamer 1"/>。他认为塞弗特“非常擅长于理解台词，在表演中直观拉动潜台词”，这让他深信她是游戏的“完美”之选<ref name="Game Mob">{{cite web |url=http://gamemob.com/news/his-story-an-interview-with-sam-barlow-creator-of-her-story/ |title=His Story: An Interview With Sam Barlow, Creator of 'Her Story' |last=Kim |first=John |work=Game Mob |publisher=Revelist Media |date=2015-07-30 |accessdate=2016-01-16 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6eZPn9t0I?url=http://gamemob.com/news/his-story-an-interview-with-sam-barlow-creator-of-her-story/ |archivedate=2016-01-16 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。巴洛吩咐塞弗特去试镜时，寄给她一本300页的剧本。他设法改变字体大小和部分对话，将台词本缩减至80页<ref name="PC Gamer 1"/>。塞弗特在拍摄中途便开始感受到压力，意识到“整部游戏都压在”她的表演上<ref name="PC Gamer 1"/>。她表示拍戏“很紧张”，“相当疲惫”，感觉自己被巴洛“暗中认真检查”，这有助于她的表演<ref name="App Unwrapper">{{cite web |url=http://www.appunwrapper.com/2015/07/10/help-interrogate-sam-barlow-about-her-story/ |title=Interrogating "Her Story" Creator Sam Barlow and Actress Viva Seifert (Interview) |page=1 |publisher=App Unwrapper |date=2015-07-10 |accessdate=2016-01-14 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6eWlsbLXV?url=http://www.appunwrapper.com/2015/07/10/help-interrogate-sam-barlow-about-her-story/ |archivedate=2016-01-14 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。巴洛还认为紧张感对塞弗特的表演十分有利，这出自为了达到最佳的表演效果经常扰乱演员的导演希区柯克<ref name="Kotaku"/>。塞弗特认为表演中的细微差别可能给玩家“增加一些”巴洛没预料到的“曲折”<ref name="App Unwrapper 2">{{cite web |url=http://www.appunwrapper.com/2015/07/10/help-interrogate-sam-barlow-about-her-story/2/ |title=Interrogating "Her Story" Creator Sam Barlow and Actress Viva Seifert (Interview) |page=2 |publisher=App Unwrapper |date=10 July 2015 |accessdate=14 January 2016 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6eWm9W5vP?url=http://www.appunwrapper.com/2015/07/10/help-interrogate-sam-barlow-about-her-story/2/ |archivedate=2016-01-14 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。七段警方审讯大致按时间顺序<ref name="PC Gamer 2"/>拍摄了五天<ref name="App Unwrapper 2"/>，这一过程在巴洛看来是“自然的”<ref name="App Unwrapper 2"/>。巴洛亲自前往塞弗特老家[[康沃尔郡|康沃尔郡]]拍戏<ref name="App Unwrapper 2"/>。他认为寻找审讯室去景点是制作中最简单的环节，“外观蹩脚的房间随处可见”，而镜头是在[[特鲁罗|特鲁罗]]议会大楼拍摄的<ref name="GamesRadar"/><ref name="PC Gamer 2"/>。拍完后，巴洛希望给视频加入一些1994年拍摄的效果，却发现[[数字滤波器|数字滤波器]]无法正确截取这一时间框架。于是在视频数字化转制入游戏前，代用两个[[VHS|VHS]]播放器录制画面，营造缺陷<ref name="Pocket Gamer"/><ref name="gamasutra road igf"/>。

拍摄期间，巴洛扮演警探询问塞弗特所演角色的剧本问题<ref name="Polygon">{{cite web |url=http://www.polygon.com/2015/7/20/8906465/her-story-ending-sam-barlow |title=Her Story creator wants the truth about the game's ending to stay a mystery |last=Farokhmanesh |first=Megan |work=Polygon |publisher=Vox Media |date=2015-07-20 |accessdate=2016-02-14 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6eWoouJfa?url=http://www.polygon.com/2015/7/20/8906465/her-story-ending-sam-barlow |archivedate=2016-01-14 |deadurl=no }}</ref>，但他没在游戏中露面<ref name="PC Gamer 2"/>。在观看警方询问研究时，巴洛发现与受访者产生了共鸣，这激发他在游戏中排除警探。他表示，询问的典型特征是“两边不得罪”，其中警探“要假装成最好的朋友”<ref name="PC Gamer 3">{{cite web |url=http://www.pcgamer.com/the-story-behind-her-story/#page-3 |title=The story behind Her Story |page=3 |last=Clark |first=Tim |work=PC Gamer |publisher=Future plc |date=2015-07-09 |accessdate=2016-01-14 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6eVfLM35W?url=http://www.pcgamer.com/the-story-behind-her-story/#page-3 |archivedate=2016-01-13 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。巴洛将警探从游戏中排除，赋予了塞弗特角色权力，使玩家感同身受<ref name="PC Gamer 3"/>。为游戏展开研究时，巴洛研讨了{{le|特拉维斯·亚历山大谋杀案|Travis Alexander}}的有关卷宗，认为女性谋杀犯应对审讯的办法表明她们“往往变得恋物，更容易原形毕露”<ref name="Pocket Gamer"/>。这一点在巴洛研究[[凯丽·安东尼之死|凯丽·安东尼]]和[[阿曼达·诺克斯|阿曼达·诺克斯]]的询问后，进一步得到证实。他认为媒体评论时常忽略调查证据，而非着眼于嫌犯在询问中的表述<ref name="LA Times">{{cite web |url=http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/herocomplex/la-et-hc-the-player-her-story-20150704-story.html |title=Head games in 'Her Story' will make you feel almost like a true detective |last=Martens |first=Todd |work=Los Angeles Times |publisher=Tribune Publishing |date=2015-07-04 |accessdate=2016-01-15 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6eXAdMzP3?url=http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/herocomplex/la-et-hc-the-player-her-story-20150704-story.html |archivedate=2016-01-14 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。巴洛继续研究心理学教材和语言运用<ref name="Gamesindustry">{{cite web |url=http://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/2015-07-10-investigating-her-story |title=Investigating Her Story |last=Horneman |first=Jurie |work=Gamesindustry.biz |publisher=Gamer Network |date=2015-07-13 |accessdate=2016-01-15 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6eYN8VP1V?url=http://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/2015-07-10-investigating-her-story |archivedate=2016-01-15 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

[[File:Her_Story_(video_game)_-_VHS_footage_development.JPG|thumb]]播放器，之后将画面转进游戏。此举能让画面精准呈现1994年的年代质感<ref name="Pocket Gamer"/>。]]

构思好游戏的主要机制后，巴洛着手开发剧情，展开研究，“使（剧情）活灵活现”<ref name="Pocket Gamer"/>。为此，巴洛将剧本写入[[电子表格|电子表格]]中，表格变得越来越大，他一打开它[[笔记本电脑|笔记本电脑]]便[[死机|死机]]<ref name="GamesRadar"/>。他列出侦查中涉及的所有角色，包括他们的背景故事和议程<ref name="Kotaku"/>。他将开发的一半时间花在制作绘制故事角色及事件详细文档上<ref name="Gamesindustry"/>，还确定了警方询问的日期和嫌犯在询问中会做的事<ref name="Kotaku"/>。一旦更为准确地确定游戏的概念，巴洛确保剧本融入“阴谋层面”，以便吸引玩家玩通关<ref name="Develop"/>。巴洛经常用同义词更改台词<ref name="Develop"/>，确保部分短片与不相关的词汇联系起来<ref name="Develop"/>。撰写剧本时，还从大局上避开[[超自然现象|超自然]]主题，但意识到“稍微梦幻的超现实优势”会掺入其中<ref name="IB Times">{{cite web |url=http://www.ibtimes.co.uk/her-story-interview-sam-barlow-storytelling-not-game-claims-1509473 |title=Her Story interview: Sam Barlow on storytelling and 'not a game' claims |last=Laverde |first=Jake |work=International Business Times |publisher=IBT Media |date=2015-07-06 |accessdate=2016-01-14 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6eWdaooMz?url=http://www.ibtimes.co.uk/her-story-interview-sam-barlow-storytelling-not-game-claims-1509473 |archivedate=2016-01-14 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。在创作剧本时，他经常发现他“以角色角度创作时文思泉涌”<ref name="Vice"/>。他发现想出新的剧情思路很难，因为侦探小说在此前已经多次探讨<ref name="Game Mob"/>。

